    class Solution {
        public String minWindow(String s, String t) {
            if (s == null || t == null || s == "" || t == "") return "";

            Map<Character, Integer> targetFreq = new HashMap<>();
            Map<Character, Integer> windowFreq = new HashMap<>();
            int match = 0;//match size
            int l = 0, r = -1;//sliding window
            int start = 0, end = s.length() + 1;

            for (Character c : t.toCharArray()) {
                targetFreq.put(c, targetFreq.getOrDefault(c, 0) + 1);
            }

            while (l < s.length()) {

                if (match < targetFreq.size()) {
                    if (r + 1 < s.length()) {
                        r++;
                        windowFreq.put(s.charAt(r), windowFreq.getOrDefault(s.charAt(r), 0) + 1);
                        if (targetFreq.containsKey(s.charAt(r)) && windowFreq.get(s.charAt(r)) == targetFreq.get(s.charAt(r))) {
                            match++;
                        }
                    } else break;
                } else {
                    if (r - l < end - start) {
                        start = l;
                        end = r;
                    }
                    windowFreq.put(s.charAt(l), windowFreq.get(s.charAt(l)) - 1);
                    if (targetFreq.containsKey(s.charAt(l)) && windowFreq.get(s.charAt(l)) < targetFreq.get(s.charAt(l))) {
                        match--;
                    }
                    l++;
                }
            }
            return end == s.length() + 1 ? "" : s.substring(start, end + 1);
        }

    }
